      <title>PJT 与新世界债券持有人举行电话会议讨论贷款事宜</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-23/pjt-holds-call-with-new-world-bondholders-on-loan-talks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，债务顾问 PJT Partners Inc. 周四与新世界发展有限公司的部分美元债券持有人举行了电话会议，讨论这家陷入困境的开发商正在进行的贷款谈判是否最终可能导致其债券违约。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-23/pjt-holds-call-with-new-world-bondholders-on-loan-talks</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 23 Jan 2025 09:42:13 GMT</pubDate>
